name: oj-rgbu-jraf-value-list
description: Displays a list of key/label and value pairs or individual messages.

values.description: An array of value entries to display. Value entries have the following properties: label - Label of the entry; value - Value of the entry; message - Alternate field to show a left-aligned message on row; This component does not require or limit you to displaying any certain number of entries; however, when rendering inside of an Info Tile, there is a limit in terms of the size of the Info Tile.
